# Setting
: https://angular.io/docs/ts/latest/guide/webpack.html
- entries - the entry-point files that define the bundles.
- resolve - how to resolve file names when they lack extensions.
            .ts extension or .js extension (for regular JavaScript files and pre-compiled TypeScript files)
- module.rules - module is an object with rules for deciding how files are loaded.
- plugins - creates instances of the plugins.

## plugins
- 파일분리: https://webpack.js.org/plugins/commons-chunk-plugin/

